      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 260,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Spatial / Environment Library\n\nThis package captures navigation, focus, and viewport semantics without pretending Twilite is already a 3D engine.\n\nV1 classes:\n- `region`\n- `anchor`\n- `portal`\n- `focus-zone`\n- `path`\n- `viewport-state`\n\nDeferred:\n- `surface`\n- `camera`\n- `cluster`\n- `landmark`",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
