      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 240,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Semantic Zoom Pressure\n\nLikely relationships:\n- `Portal` links spatial regions\n- `Anchor` marks stable points\n- `Path` connects regions or anchors\n- `Focus Zone` influences viewport behavior\n\nKeep it tied to navigation and focus.",
